{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MathML 属性リファレンス","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>これは MathML 属性のアルファベット順リストです。各属性の詳細はそれぞれの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element\" title=\"/docs/MathML/Element\">要素のページ</a> にあります。</p>\n\n<p>補足:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>MathML <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code> 要素と <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>  要素は、すべての MathML プレゼンテーション要素のすべての属性を受け入れます。</li>\n <li>MathML の値と単位についての補足は、<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">値 (en-US)</a> を参照してください。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th>属性名</th>\n   <th>この属性を取る要素</th>\n   <th>説明</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr id=\"accent\">\n   <td><code>accent</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\" title=\"<mover>\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munderover&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>演算子がアクセント記号として扱われるべきか否かを指定する真偽値。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"accentunder\">\n   <td><code>accentunder</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\" title=\"<munder>\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munderover&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>演算子がアクセント記号として扱われるべきか否かを指定する真偽値。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"actiontype\">\n   <td><code>actiontype</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;maction&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>この要素で起こるアクションを指定する文字列値。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"align\">\n   <td><code>align</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code><br>\n    <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\" title=\"<munder>\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\" title=\"<mover>\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munderover&gt; (en-US)</a></code><br>\n    <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>いくつかの要素の揃える位置を指定する (詳細は要素のページを参照)。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"alignmentscope\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>alignmentscope</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>テーブル列が整列スコープとして振る舞うか否かを指定する真偽値。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"alt-*\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span><br>\n    <code>altimg</code><br>\n    <code>altimg-width</code><br>\n    <code>altimg-height</code><br>\n    <code>altimg-valign</code><br>\n    <code>alttext</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>視覚的およびテキストへのフォールバックオプション。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"bevelled\">\n   <td><code>bevelled</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"<mfrac>\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>分数がどのように表示されるべきかを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"charalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>charalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>桁の水平方向の揃えを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"close\">\n   <td><code>close</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\" title=\"<mfenced>\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>閉じデリミタの文字列。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnalign\">\n   <td><code>columnalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"<mtd>\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\" title=\"<mtr>\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlabeledtr\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlabeledtr&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表のセルの水平方向の揃えを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnlines\">\n   <td><code>columnlines</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表の列間罫線を指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnspacing\">\n   <td><code>columnspacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表の列間スペースを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnspan\">\n   <td><code>columnspan</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"<mtd>\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表のセルが何列分を占めるかを指定する非負整数。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnwidth\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>columnwidth</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表の列の幅を指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"crossout\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>crossout</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarry\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarry&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies what kind of line is drawn to cross out carries.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"decimalpoint\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>decimalpoint</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>If the <code>decimalpoint</code> value is used to specify the <a href=\"#align\">alignment</a>, this attribute is specifying the character for the alignment point within <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code> and <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code> columns.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"denomalign\">\n   <td><code>denomalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"<mfrac>\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>分数の分母の揃え方。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"depth\">\n   <td><code>depth</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Sets or increments the depth. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">length (en-US)</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"dir\">\n   <td><code>dir</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"<mi>\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mrow&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\" title=\"<mtext>\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>The text direction. Possible values are either ltr (left to right) or rtl (right to left).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"display\">\n   <td><code>display</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>レンダリングモードを指定する。取り得る値は <code>block</code> と <code>inline</code>。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"displaystyle\">\n   <td><code>displaystyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value specifying whether more vertical space is used for displayed equations or, if set to <code>false</code>, a more compact layout is used to display formulas.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"edge\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>edge</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/malignmark\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;malignmark&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"equalcolumns\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>equalcolumns</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value indicating whether to force all columns to have the same total height.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"equalrows\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>equalrows</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value indicating whether to force all rows to have the same total height.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"fence\">\n   <td><code>fence</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value specifying whether the operator is a fence (such as parentheses). There is no visual effect for this attribute.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"form\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>form</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the role of the operator in an enclosed expression.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"frame\">\n   <td><code>frame</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies borders of an entire <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code>. Possible values are: <code>none</code> (default), <code>solid</code> and <code>dashed</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"framespacing\">\n   <td><code>framespacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies additional space added between the table and <code>frame</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"groupalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>groupalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maligngroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;maligngroup&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"<mtd>\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\" title=\"<mtr>\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"height\">\n   <td><code>height</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mglyph\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mglyph&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the desired height. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">lengths (en-US)</a> for possible values.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"href\">\n   <td><code>href</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>Used to set a hyperlink to a specified URI.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"id\">\n   <td><code>id</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>Sets up a unique identifier associated with the element.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>indentalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentalignfirst\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>indentalignfirst</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentalignlast\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>indentalignlast</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentshift\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>indentshift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentshiftfirst\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>indentshiftfirst</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentshiftlast\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>indentshiftlast</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indenttarget\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>indenttarget</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"infixlinebreakstyle\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>infixlinebreakstyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the default <code>linebreakstyle</code> to use for infix operators.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"largeop\">\n   <td><code>largeop</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>演算子が通常よりも大きく書かれるべきかを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"length\">\n   <td><code>length</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msline\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msline&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linebreak\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>linebreak</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linebreakmultchar\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>linebreakmultchar</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linebreakstyle\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>linebreakstyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"lineleading\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>lineleading</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linethickness\">\n   <td><code>linethickness</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"<mfrac>\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>水平分数線の幅</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"location\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>location</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarries\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarries&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"longdivstyle\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>longdivstyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlongdiv\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlongdiv&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>割り算の筆算レイアウトのスタイルを制御する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"lspace\">\n   <td><code>lspace</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>演算子の前側の空き量 (値と単位は <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">length (en-US)</a> を参照)。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"lquote\">\n   <td><code>lquote</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>コンテンツを囲む引用開始文字 (<code>dir</code> に依存します)。デフォルト値は、\"<code>&amp;quot;</code>\"。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathbackground\">\n   <td><code>mathbackground</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>背景色。<code>#rgb</code> および <code>#rrggbb</code>、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#html.2fsvg.2fx11.c2.a0_color_keywords\">HTML カラー名</a> が使用できます。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathcolor\">\n   <td><code>mathcolor</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>テキスト色。<code>#rgb</code> および <code>#rrggbb</code>、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#html.2fsvg.2fx11.c2.a0_color_keywords\">HTML カラー名</a> が使用できます。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathsize\">\n   <td><code>mathsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"<mi>\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\" title=\"<mn>\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\" title=\"<mtext>\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>コンテンツのサイズ。Gecko 20.0 (Firefox 20 / Thunderbird 20 / SeaMonkey 2.17) 以降、単位無しの値が使用でき、デフォルト値の N 倍の値として解釈されます。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathvariant\">\n   <td><code>mathvariant</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"<mi>\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\" title=\"<mn>\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\" title=\"<mtext>\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>識別子の論理クラス。タイポグラフィーによって様々です。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"maxsize\">\n   <td><code>maxsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>演算子の最大サイズ。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"minlabelspacing\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>minlabelspacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">length value (en-US)</a> specifing the minimum space between a <a href=\"Element/mlabeledtr\" rel=\"internal\">label</a> and the adjacent cell in the row.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"minsize\">\n   <td><code>minsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>演算子の最小サイズ。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"movablelimits\">\n   <td><code>movablelimits</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies whether attached under- and overscripts move to sub- and superscript positions.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"notation\">\n   <td><code>notation</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;menclose&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A list of notations, separated by white space, to apply to the child elements.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"numalign\">\n   <td><code>numalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"<mfrac>\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>分数の分子の揃え方。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"open\">\n   <td><code>open</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\" title=\"<mfenced>\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>開きデリミタの文字列。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"overflow\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>overflow</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>If an expression is too long to fit in the allowed width, this attribute sets the preferred handling.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"position\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>position</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msgroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msgroup&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msrow\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msrow&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarries\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarries&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msline\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msline&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowalign\">\n   <td><code>rowalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"<mtd>\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\" title=\"<mtr>\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表のセルの垂直方向の揃えを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowlines\">\n   <td><code>rowlines</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表の行間罫線を指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowspacing\">\n   <td><code>rowspacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表の行間スペースを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowspan\">\n   <td><code>rowspan</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"<mtd>\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>表のセルが何行分を占めるかを指定する非負整数。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rspace\">\n   <td><code>rspace</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>演算子の後ろ側の空き量。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rquote\">\n   <td><code>rquote</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>コンテンツを囲む引用終了文字 (<code>dir</code> に依存します)。デフォルト値は、\"<code>&amp;quot;</code>\"。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"scriptlevel\">\n   <td><code>scriptlevel</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Controls mostly the font-size. The higher the <code>scriptlevel</code>, the smaller the font size.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"scriptminsize\">\n   <td><code>scriptminsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies a minimum font size allowed due to changes in <code>scriptlevel</code>.<br>\n    Starting with Gecko 20.0 (Firefox 20 / Thunderbird 20 / SeaMonkey 2.17) unitless values and percent values are allowed and interpreted as multiple of \"8pt\".</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"scriptsizemultiplier\">\n   <td><code>scriptsizemultiplier</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the multiplier to be used to adjust font size due to changes in <code>scriptlevel</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"selection\">\n   <td><code>selection</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;maction&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The child element which is addressed by the action.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"separator\">\n   <td><code>separator</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>視覚的には変わらないが，演算子が区切り記号（カンマなど）であるか否かを指定する。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"separators\">\n   <td><code>separators</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\" title=\"<mfenced>\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>区切り記号として使うゼロ個以上の文字の列</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"shift\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>shift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msgroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msgroup&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"side\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>side</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the position where <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlabeledtr\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlabeledtr&gt;</a></code> label elements should be placed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"src\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>src</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mglyph\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mglyph&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>画像リソースの場所</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"stackalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未実装</span> <code>stackalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"stretchy\">\n   <td><code>stretchy</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies whether the operator stretches to the size of the adjacent element.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"subscriptshift\">\n   <td><code>subscriptshift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"<mmultiscripts>\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\" title=\"<msub>\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" title=\"<msubsup>\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>The minimum space by which to shift the subscript below the baseline of the expression.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"supscriptshift\">\n   <td><code>supscriptshift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"<mmultiscripts>\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" title=\"<msup>\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" title=\"<msubsup>\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>The minimum space by which to shift the superscript above the baseline of the expression.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"symmetric\">\n   <td><code>symmetric</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>If <code>stretchy</code> is <code>true</code>, this attribute specifies whether the operator should be vertically symmetric around the imaginary math axis (centered fraction line).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"voffset\">\n   <td><code>voffset</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Sets the vertical position of the child content.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"width\">\n   <td><code>width</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mglyph\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mglyph&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the desired width. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">lengths (en-US)</a> for possible values.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"xlink-href\">\n   <td><code>xlink:href</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>Can be used to set a hyperlink to a specfied URI. However, authors are encouraged to use the <code>href</code> attribute instead.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"xmlns\">\n   <td><code>xmlns</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>MathML 名前空間の URI (<code><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" rel=\"freelink noopener\">http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML</a></code>) を指定する</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"これは MathML 属性のアルファベット順リストです。各属性の詳細はそれぞれの 要素のページ にあります。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MathML Attribut-Referenz","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"MathML attribute reference","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MathML attribute reference","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Référence des attributs MathML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Справка по атрибутам MathML","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"MathML attribute reference","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mathml/attribute","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/mathml/attribute/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute","title":"MathML 属性リファレンス"}],"pageTitle":"MathML 属性リファレンス - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}